node.text:
FROM THE VAULT: Still locked down in quarantine, we dug through our archives to bring you this never-before-seen footage from our recurring series where we put customer testimonials to the test. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
In this special edition, we didn't just run over a brand new Samsung #GalaxyS10 with a 1933 Ford #roadster with a Hemi motor. We chucked it out the window of a 1933 #Ford roadster with a #Hemi motor going 60 mph, too #toughlikeyou #supmycase #supcasestories

Special thanks to @gatewayclassiccars

node.title: We Ran Over A Galaxy S10 Then Threw It Out the Window

node.text:
The rhinoceros horn is the highest commodity in the world per weight. And each day, 3 rhinoceros are poached for their horn.⁣
⁣
That’s why Nina Kubicek from @rhoveafrica is on a mission to raise awareness about this ongoing crisis. ⁣
⁣
Join us in helping save the rhino by sharing Nina’s story. To do our part, we have agreed to match Nina in donating $500 US (or R8,250) to @careforwild, and $500 to @zululand_rhino_orphanage in South Africa. BUT — every little bit helps.⁣
⁣
To find out how you can help, follow @rhoveafrica #savetherhino #careforwild #zululandrhinoorphanage #rhino #rhinoconservation #rhinorescue #supcasestories

@smoked.media proves the #UBElectro clear case is every bit as tough as the award-winning #UBPro:⁣⁣
⁣⁣
"Hello, I wanted to share a video of an incident I had today on my motorcycle. I was doing about 70 mph when my phone fell off my bike. It got ran over a couple of times. I thought for sure my phone was going to be shattered, but aside from some road rash on the case, everything is fine."⁣⁣
⁣⁣
NSFW audio at 01:16 🤣 #motorcycle #bike #biker #supmycase #toughlikeyou

node.text:
What happens when we throw a #Galaxy #S10 out the window at 60 mph? Since winning @CNET's annual drop test with the highest total feet, the #UnicornBeetlePro has achieved legendary status. From getting run over by classic cars and shielding an undercover officer from gunshots, to surviving a 150 ft drop from a helicopter over South African plains, the UB Pro continues to get put to the test—and passes every time.⁣
⁣
To ensure our cases can stand up to even our toughest fans, part of our testing is to push our cases to the limit and see how far we have to go to break a phone (including chucking it out the window at 100 km/h). The boring truth is...we haven't broken a phone yet 🤷 #supcasestories #supmycase #galaxys10

node.title: Throwing Galaxy S10 Out Window at 60 MPH
